Host (Landlord) Module
1. Property Management
    Create new property listings
    Edit property information
    Upload and manage property images
    Set pricing and occupancy limits
    Manage amenities and house rules
    Activate or deactivate property listings

2. Booking & Reservation Management
    View booking requests
    Approve or reject reservations
    Track active and upcoming bookings
    Monitor completed reservations
    Handle booking cancellations
    View reservation history

3. Availability & Calendar Management
    Manage property availability
    Block dates for maintenance or personal use
    View booked and available dates
    Prevent overlapping reservations
    Maintain reservation schedules

4. Guest Management
    View guest profiles
    Monitor guest booking history
    Access guest reviews and ratings
    Track guest activities
    Manage guest communication records

5. Revenue & Earnings Management
    Track booking revenue
    Monitor monthly and annual earnings
    View payout history
    Generate financial reports
    Analyze property performance

6. Reviews & Ratings Management
    View guest reviews
    Respond to guest feedback
    Monitor property ratings
    Track customer satisfaction

7. Messaging & Communication
    Communicate with guests
    Manage booking inquiries
    Receive reservation notifications
    Handle guest concerns and requests

8. Account & Profile Management
    Update host profile information
    Manage contact details
    Change password and security settings
    Configure notification preferences

